   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Avina Paraguay</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Although it has representations in each country, Fundaci&#xF3;n Avina in the Chaco region contributes to the Alliance providing an unifying vision of the Biome shared by the two countries (Bolivia and Paraguay). This has helped to strengthen the coordinated work with WWF. In Paraguay, Fundaci&#xF3;n Avina contributes its work experience in the construction of public policies with local governments in key aspects for adaptation to climate change in the region, prioritizing the rescue of knowledge from both indigenous and non-indigenous communities through the strengthening of work with women&apos;s groups and indigenous community communicators.</narrative>
  </description>
